description: Welcome to this rare opportunity to own a condo just steps from Chicago's iconic Millennium Park, with views of Lake Michigan. This bright unit offers a premier location in the heart of downtown, surrounded by world-class dining, entertainment, and cultural attractions.  Enjoy resort-style amenities including a 24-hour doorman, fitness center, indoor pool, sundeck, business center, library, resident lounge and so much more. A modular, smart layout, this condo is a perfect canvas for your personal touch, offering renovation potential to transform it into a modern urban retreat.    Whether you're seeking a primary residence, weekend getaway, or investment property, this home combines unbeatable location, panoramic water views, and exceptional building features in one of Chicago's most coveted addresses.
